---
title: Fillet Steak & Onion-Peppercorn Sauce with Truffle Fries & Garlicky Greens
description: There’s something eternally comforting about the aroma of a creamy peppercorn sauce. Completely mouth-watering to say the least. Drizzled over tender premium fillet steak with a side of nutty greens and umami-rich truffle fries, it’s time for pub-style steak and chips to move over; there’s a new and completely luxe contender in town.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fillet-steak-onion-peppercorn-sauce-0740703f.jpg
